snippet.title: 33 Immortals - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover 33 Immortals, a co-op action-roguelike for 33 players.
Coming 2024 on Xbox Series X|S, Windows PC and with Xbox Game Pass for console and PC.

33 Immortals is a co-op action-roguelike for 33 players. Play a damned soul, and rebel against God's final judgement. Dive straight into epic 33-player co-op battles with instant “pick-up and raid” matchmaking. Cooperate with your allies to survive against hordes of monsters and massive, challenging bosses. Expand your arsenal and equip powerful new relics to permanently upgrade your soul. Face the wrath of God in a fight for your eternal life.

Subscribe to Xbox: 🎮 https://xbx.lv/2EEjmaR

Follow Xbox in other channels:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Xbox
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/Xbox
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/Xbox
